nodes.text: Oulanne was a jungle planet in the Inner Rim of the the galaxy.

During a mission for the Alliance to Restore the Republic in 1 BBY, a special operative team, including Jan Ors, stole a cargo of prime-grade fuel slugs from the Galactic Empire in the jungles of Oulanne. During the mission, Ors contracted a type of disease from the jungles that infected her right leg, causing delirium.
